M|kai|- MRR growth is the primary financial signal; monitor cohort MRR, not blended MRR
M|kai|- Trial-to-paid rate is the highest-leverage conversion metric — flag any drop immediately
M|kai|- DAU/MAU < 0.20 signals an activation problem, not an acquisition problem — fix before scaling
M|kai|- Tier match: early-stage fintech/budgeting apps (similar MAU range)
M|kai|- Flag: never cite Mint, YNAB, or bank apps as direct cp without tier qualification
M|kai|- LinkedIn organic reach peaks Tue–Thu, 8–10am local time
